* perceval-mozilla 0.3.5
* perceval-opnfv 0.2.5
* perceval-puppet 0.2.5
* perceval-weblate 0.2.5
* kingarthur 0.2.5
* graal 0.4.2
* grimoire-elk 0.103.3
* sirmordred 0.5.1

The following list describes the changes by component:

### sortinghat
  
  * Update Poetry's package dependencies

